passages.text: Hmm. I see ya Guppy. How can I be of service to ya?[[Good question?|services]][[What are you up to over here?|services]]

links.name: What are you up to over here?|services
links.link: What are you up to over here?|services

passages.text:
Ya see, sometimes folks drag somethin' out of the sea that the other vendors don't wholly appreciate. And they want to sell it. And sometimes they might not want the Church knowin' it was caught. That's where I come in.
[[Sell]][[Leave]]
passages.name: services

passages.text: Aye, return when ya have something worthy of my coin.
passages.name: Leave
